  " Keyboard (re)mappings ▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁▁

    " .................................................................... Setup

      let mapleader   = "\<Space>"          " remap <leader> a la spacemacs
      let g:mapleader = "\<Space>"

      " unshift command mode
      " nnoremap ; :
      " vnoremap ; :
      " shift (not applied as requires global usage of noremap for :command)
      " nnoremap : ;
